schemas.name: api_client_logging
schemas.description: Whether to print logs from the API client (using the default log library logger)

schemas.name: max_backoff
schemas.description: Maximum backoff period in seconds after failed API calls

schemas.name: min_backoff
schemas.description: Minimum backoff period in seconds after failed API calls

schemas.name: org_id
schemas.description: Configure API client to always use that organization. If set this will override 'user_owner_from_zone'

schemas.name: retries
schemas.description: Maximum number of retries to perform when an API request fails

schemas.name: rps
schemas.description: RPS limit to apply when making calls to the API

schemas.name: token
schemas.description: The token key for API operations.

schemas.name: use_org_from_zone
schemas.description: If specified zone is owned by an organization, configure API client to always use that organization
